printer_notes.3.0.0:
Dont remove the following keywords! These keywords are used in the "compatible printer" condition of the print and filament profiles to link the particular print and filament profiles to this printer profile.
PRINTER_VENDOR_MAKERGEAR
PRINTER_MODEL_MAKERGEAR_U1

end_gcode.3.0.0:
M106 P2 S0 ; turn off exhaust fan
 
M104 S0 ; turn off extruder
M104 S0 T0 ; turn off extruder
M104 S0 T1; turn off extruder
M140 P0 S0 ; turn off bed
M140 P1 S0 ; turn off bed
M140 P2 S0 ; turn off bed
M140 P3 S0 ; turn off bed
M106 S0 ; turn off cooling fan
G91 ; relative mode
G1 Z20 ; move Z down 20mm
G90;  absolute mode

G28 XY ; home tool/s
M502 ; set to firmware default values
T0 ; defualt tool should always be T0

start_gcode.3.0.0:
;U1 Startup Script

M203 X18000.00 Y18000.00 Z1200.00 U18000.00 E1800.00 ; U1 max feedrate mm/minute
        M201 X1200 Y1200 Z10 U1200 E2000             ; U1 Maximum Acceleration axes mm/s^2
        M204 P2000 T2000                             ; U1 Maximum Acceleration printing / travel mm/s^2
        M566 X300 Y300 Z60 U300 E600                 ; U1  instantenous speed change 'jerk' in mm/minute
        M593 F0                                      ; make sure dynamix acceleration is off 

; Turn off hotends to reduce ooze on the bed during startup
M104 T0 S0
M104 T1 S0
; Note: this will not explicitly wait for the hotends to cool down

M221 D0 S100  ; Extruder rate for T0 is set in the profile so set to 100%
M221 D1 S100  ; Extruder rate for T1 is set in the profile so set to 100%

{if first_layer_bed_temperature[1] < first_layer_bed_temperature[0]}
M140 P0 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]}	     ; Middle bed heater strip
M140 P1 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]}	     ; 2nd from left and second from right bed heater
M140 P2 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]}	     ; Left bed heater strip
M140 P3 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]}	     ; Right bed heater strip
{endif}

{if first_layer_bed_temperature[0] < first_layer_bed_temperature[1]}
M140 P0 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[1]}	     ; Middle bed heater strip
M140 P1 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[1]}	     ; 2nd from left and second from right bed heater
M140 P2 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[1]}	     ; Left bed heater strip
M140 P3 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[1]}	     ; Right bed heater strip
{endif}

M116 ; Wait for all bed heating pads to reach operation temperature before homing (this will wait for cooldown if there is overshoot)
G28  ; 1)Home XY,  2)Home Z,  3)Auto Level,  4)Home Z,  5) Mesh Level

; Set hotend temperature
M104 T0 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}
M104 T1 S{first_layer_temperature[1]}

; Wait for hotends to reach temperature
M109 T0 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}
M109 T1 S{first_layer_temperature[1]}

M116 ; Wait for all hotends to reach operation temperature (this will wait for cooldown if there is overshoot)

; Purge Scripts
{if temperature[1] == 0}
; U1 Single Mode - Left Purge
T0 		    ; implied by G28 but explicilty called here
G1 Z20.0 F6000      ; Move Z to 20
G92 E0              ; Zero Extruder
M564 S0 	    ; Safteys off
G1 X160 Y5 F1000    ; Move to unused front edge
G1 Z0.30 F1000      ; Move closer to the bed
G1 X40 E20 F1000    ; Deposit purge line
G1 X30 Z0.05 F1000  ; Wipe off tail
G1 Z10		    ; Move away from bed
G1 Y11 		    ; Move to Y-axis safe zone
G92 E0 	            ; Zero extruder
M564 S0 	    ; Safteys off
M106 P2 S50         ; Enable exhaust fan
{endif}

{if temperature[0] == 0}
; U1 Single Mode - Right Purge
T1		    ; Switch to T1
G1 Z20.0 F6000      ; Move Z to 20
G92 E0              ; Zero Extruder
M564 S0 	    ; Safteys off
G1 X160 Y5 F1000    ; Move to unused front edge
G1 Z0.30 F1000      ; Move closer to the bed
G1 X40 E20 F1000    ; Deposit purge line
G1 X30 Z0.05 F1000  ; Wipe off tail
G1 Z10		    ; Move away from bed
G1 Y11 		    ; Move to y safe zone
G92 E0 		    ; Zero extruder
M564 S0             ; Safteys off
M106 P2 S50         ; Enable exhaust fan
{endif}

{if temperature[0] > 0 && temperature[1] > 0}
; U1 T0/T1 Startup Script
T1 		    ; Switch to T1
G1 Z20.0 F6000      ; Move Z to 20
G92 E0              ; Zero Extruder
M564 S0 	    ; Safteys off
G1 X160 Y5 F1000    ; Move to unused front edge
G1 Z0.30 F1000      ; Move closer to the bed
G1 X40 E20 F1000    ; Deposit purge line
G1 X30 Z0.05 F1000  ; Wipe off tail
G1 Z10		    ; Move away from bed
G1 Y11 		    ; Move to y safe zone
G92 E0 		    ; Zero extruder

T0		    ; Switch to T0
G1 X360 Y5 F1000    ; Move to unused front edge
G1 Z0.30 F1000      ; Move closer to the bed
G1 X240 E20 F1000   ; Deposit purge line
G1 X230 Z0.05 F1000 ; Wipe off tail
G1 Z10		    ; Move away from bed
G1 Y11 		    ; Move to y safe zone
G92 E0 		    ; Zero extruder
M564 S1 	    ; Safteys on
M106 P2 S50         ; Enable exhaust fan
{endif}
